  "detailed_description": "<u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Warm tips: the game only supports mouse and keyboard, not handle controller</strong></h2></u><br>Players in the game can enter the battlefield at any time to fight you, and the attributes among players are balanced<br><br>You can grab other players' equipment in the game, or go to the survival circle to grab supplies<br><br>You can also buy all the equipment and food before entering the battlefield<br><br>As long as you kill any creature, you will get gold coin, which is the only currency in the game<br><br>There are many ways to get gold coins, such as killing others, killing zombies, killing boss and completing daily tasks<br><br>The big map in the game is your strategic skill of using wisdom<br><br>Gather enough gold coins to buy a fashion box and get a better look<br><br>Even buy a powerful power weapon. It's a weapon with special attack skills. It's gorgeous and cool!<br><br>In order to speed up the action, you can also buy a mount to get to the target quickly<br><br>Remember, the fight about this game will never stop as long as you live",
  "about_the_game": "<u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Warm tips: the game only supports mouse and keyboard, not handle controller</strong></h2></u><br>Players in the game can enter the battlefield at any time to fight you, and the attributes among players are balanced<br><br>You can grab other players' equipment in the game, or go to the survival circle to grab supplies<br><br>You can also buy all the equipment and food before entering the battlefield<br><br>As long as you kill any creature, you will get gold coin, which is the only currency in the game<br><br>There are many ways to get gold coins, such as killing others, killing zombies, killing boss and completing daily tasks<br><br>The big map in the game is your strategic skill of using wisdom<br><br>Gather enough gold coins to buy a fashion box and get a better look<br><br>Even buy a powerful power weapon. It's a weapon with special attack skills. It's gorgeous and cool!<br><br>In order to speed up the action, you can also buy a mount to get to the target quickly<br><br>Remember, the fight about this game will never stop as long as you live",
